{
  "slug": "skill-creator",
  "name": "Skill Creator",
  "type": "plugin",
  "description": "Create new skills, improve existing skills, and measure skill performance. Use when users want to create a skill from scratch, update or optimize an existing skill, run evals to test a skill, or benchmark skill performance with variance analysis.",
  "longDescription": "Plugin wrapping the official Anthropic `skill-creator` skill with **4 agents** (analyzer, comparator, executor, grader), **8 Python scripts** (`init_skill.py`, `copy_skill.py`, `package_skill.py`, `prepare_eval.py`, `quick_validate.py`, `validate_json.py`, `init_json.py`, `aggregate_benchmark.py`), and **4 reference docs** covering eval mode, benchmark mode, mode diagrams, and JSON schemas. Supports creating skills from scratch, running structured evals with test cases, and benchmarking skill performance with variance analysis across multiple runs.",
